history.p: The autograph printer's manuscript is dated 25 June 1907. In a letter on the same day, Nielsen mentions having composed the song. In an interview (Nationaltidende, 1918), however, Nielsen revealed that he was working on it for a period of three to four months before being satisfied with it.
